description: Number of labeled pure 2-complexes on n nodes (0-simplexes) with 5 2-simplexes and 13 1-simplexes.
comments: Number of {T_1,T_2,...,T_k} where T_i,i=1..k are 3-subsets of an n-set such that {D | D is 2-subset of T_i for some i=1..k} has l elements; k=5,l=13.
references: V. Jovovic, On the number of two-dimensional simplicial complexes (in Russian), Metody i sistemy tekhnicheskoy diagnostiki, Vypusk 16, Mezhvuzovskiy zbornik nauchnykh trudov, Izdatelstvo Saratovskogo universiteta, 1991.
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Apr 10 2000
